review_title: A dam site better than I expected!
one_reviews_text:
1st Impressions Video with Commentary // Oculus Rift S // GTX 1060 (6GB):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ux7AwNGo5MM

My Initial Impressions:
This turned out to be quite interesting and fun, a lot better than I was expecting to be honest and I certainly was not expecting the progression in the game.
My only gripe is.... In VR I have 2 hands, why can't I use both hands to model the clay?

Always glad to see more product for a more mature audience.  Very creative and I am enjoying the progression of the game!  My only ask would be to enable the right hand for an even more realistic experience,  Good job!
